data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COST ! This spacious all brick ranch home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a comfortable 1,537 square feet of living space. Renovated in 2019, it offers modern amenities and style. Inside, you will find a large living room, a separate dining area, and a versatile bonus room that can serve as an office, playroom, or den. The kitchen is well-equipped with stainless steel appliances, perfect for all your culinary adventures. The living areas feature attractive laminated flooring, while the bedrooms offer plush carpeting for added comfort. Step outside into the large fenced-in backyard, an ideal space for outdoor activities and your furry companions. The property's prime location is just a three-minute drive from the front gate of Fort Stewart, making it exceptionally convenient for military personnel. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your new home sweet home.
